      "text": "AWS KMS protects your root keys.\nKMS keys are created, managed, used,\nand deleted entirely within AWS KMS.\nThey never leave the service unencrypted. ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "AWS KMS protects your root keys.\nKMS keys are created, managed, used,\nand deleted entirely within AWS KMS.\nThey never leave the service unencrypted. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
