      "text": "AWS WAF works with:\n    Amazon CloudFront\n    Application Load Balancer (ALB)\n    API Gateway\n    AWS AppSync\nIt sits between the internet and your application.",
      "fontSize": 20.106665039062502,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "AWS WAF works with:\n    Amazon CloudFront\n    Application Load Balancer (ALB)\n    API Gateway\n    AWS AppSync\nIt sits between the internet and your application.",
