      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772360274503,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "🔷 What Data Does GuardDuty Monitor?\n\nGuardDuty analyzes multiple AWS logs:\n1️⃣ VPC Flow Logs\n→ Detect suspicious network traffic.\n2️⃣ CloudTrail Logs\n→ Detect unusual API activity.\n3️⃣ DNS Logs\n→ Detect connections to malicious domains.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🔷 What Data Does GuardDuty Monitor?\n\nGuardDuty analyzes multiple AWS logs:\n1️⃣ VPC Flow Logs\n→ Detect suspicious network traffic.\n2️⃣ CloudTrail Logs\n→ Detect unusual API activity.\n3️⃣ DNS Logs\n→ Detect connections to malicious domains.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
