      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772360618090,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How it works-->\n\n1️⃣ AWS collects logs (CloudTrail, DNS, VPC Flow Logs)\n2️⃣ GuardDuty analyzes traffic patterns\n3️⃣ Detects suspicious activity\n4️⃣ Generates a Security Finding\n5️⃣ Alerts the security team",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How it works-->\n\n1️⃣ AWS collects logs (CloudTrail, DNS, VPC Flow Logs)\n2️⃣ GuardDuty analyzes traffic patterns\n3️⃣ Detects suspicious activity\n4️⃣ Generates a Security Finding\n5️⃣ Alerts the security team",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
